title: Are tech giants 'sunsetting'? Strategists warn of big tech under pressure - CNBC
content: Are tech giants 'sunsetting'? Strategists warn of big tech under pressure  CNBC
description: Investors looking at tech giants in both the U.S. and China need to be cautious, as these firms are facing a myriad of issues, a couple of investment managers told CNBC this week.
